hyperpage provides CMake targets:

    find_package(hyperpage CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE hyperpage::hyperpage)

hyperpage also provides the hyperpack command-line utility:

    hyperpack [--output <file>] [--verbose] <directories>...

    Packs files from the specified directories into a hyperpage SQLite database.
    The default output file is "hyperpage.db".
